           move event-data-2 to riga.
           if riga < 2 
              move 2 to riga
           end-if.

           modify gd-log, start-x = 1,    x = 7,
                          start-y = riga, y = riga,
                          region-color 481 
           .
      * <TOTEM:END>

       PARAGRAFO-COPY.
